        <p>
          Satellite-based network infrastructure for hospitals, institutions, businesses,
          and remote sites across Africa, including billing and operations support.
        </p>
      </div>

      <div class="footer-block">
        <h2>Pages</h2>
        <ul class="footer-list">
          <li><a href="/">Home</a></li>
          <li><a href="/about">About</a></li>
          <li><a href="/contact">Contact</a></li>
          <li><a href="/join-waitlist">Partner page</a></li>
          <li><a href="/cookies">Cookies policy</a></li>
        </ul>
      </div>

      <div class="footer-block">
        <h2>Contact</h2>
        <ul class="footer-list">
          <li>Nairobi, Kenya</li>
          <li><a href="mailto:hello@cloudbridge.network">hello@cloudbridge.network</a></li>
